2006;;The Beach Party at the Threshold of Hell;;American;;Kevin Wheatley, Jonny Gilette;;Kevin Wheatley, Bill English;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Beach_Party_at_the_Threshold_of_Hell;;The film is set in New America in the year 2097, two decades after a nuclear apocalypse. Tex Kennedy, the last survivor of the Kennedy family, two robotic ex-secret service agents, and a female cannibal journey to find the "Threshold of Hell" to gain access to a radio tower to unite the survivors of the apocalypse.[1]